---

## ⚡ Systemd Cheat Sheet

- Start: `systemctl start genlayernode`
- Stop: `systemctl stop genlayernode`
- Logs: `journalctl -u genlayernode -f`
- Backup timer status: `systemctl list-timers | grep genlayer`

